snippet.title: Angry Birds Go!
snippet.description: With familiar characters, drift-racing action, and good-looking graphics, Angry Birds Go! is a fun arcade racer, but repetitive gameplay and freemium limitations are regrettably part of the package.

snippet.title: Neato XV-21
snippet.description: The XV-21 is a great all-around robot vacuum and a viable Roomba alternative, but among Neatos, we'll stick with the brainier, similarly priced XV Signature Pro.

snippet.title: Plantronics BackBeat Go 2 stereo Bluetooth headset
snippet.description: While its short battery life keeps it from true greatness, the Plantronics BackBeat Go 2 is a superior wireless Bluetooth in-ear headphone.

snippet.title: Peace, quiet, and a love hotel for your soul in New York
snippet.description: An app called Breather is like AirBnB for a peaceful corner of a big city. It uses space in office buildings that can be rented by the hour.

snippet.title: Foursquare for Windows Phone
snippet.description: Even though Foursquare for Windows Phone's design can be overwhelming at first, it's an essential app for finding local attractions.

snippet.description: This year's New York auto show saw a slew of everyday, practical cars, but also featured a streak of passion.

snippet.title: Plantronics BackBeat Go 2 + Charging Case stereo Bluetooth headset
